  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "In Philosoma, you blast through 18 vertical scrolling deep space environments in search of the mysterious distress call, destroying enemies and obstacles in your path.\n\nGo up against a variety of vehicles including the \"Hover Carrier,\" the \"Makkon,\" and the \"Missile Walker\" as you clear your way with one of four main weapons such as the Vulcan, Laser, A-Break, or Ray-B. Each weapon can be upgraded up to three times when specific power-up icons are collected. A secondary weapon such as Buster grenades, MRMs, and SRMs are equipped at the beginning of a level or acquired through a power-up.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Communication Interrupt > Message Follows\nAlpha Priority Distress . Repeat. Priority Distress ORA-194-220 . {Break} Installation Under ATT {Break} Unknown Source.\n\nAttention - Crew of UNF Galant\n>>All Strega Pilots Prepare To Launch > Mission: Break Through Enemy Lines And Neutralize Unknown Threat.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
